<td class="d-block comment-body markdown-body  js-comment-body">

          <p>Instead of logging in on every app start (after the one hour) the app should request refresh tokens. For that I would need to change to the Authorization Code Flow and have a backend where I request these because it needs to access the client secret.</p>
